	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l957" cert="high">Pinsoviae</placeName> 4. novembris 1557.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutem in domino nostro Iesu Christo perpetuam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non dubito, domine et amice longium omnium charissime, quin anxio solicitoque animo expectes nuntium laetum de meo salvo in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Poloniam</placeName> adventu.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8354" cert="high">Laetus</persName>, salvis incolumisque dei optimi maximi benefitio ante octiduum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracoviam</placeName> veni et a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracovia</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l957" cert="high">Pinzoviam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName ref="p8041" cert="high">Ioannem a Lasco</persName> virum omnibus modis observandum tuique amantissimum salvum reperi.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Is me propter commendationes tuas perhumaniter accepit causamque meam diligenter apud ducem palatinumque <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l552" cert="high">Vilnensem</placeName> per literas egit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Privilegium me consequturum non dubito.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proinde hinc recta <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l552" cert="high">Vilnam</placeName> ad ducem ipsum et regiam maiestatem post paucos dies profecturus sum.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Comitem itineris d. <persName type="auto_name">Guilhelmum Marlo</persName> olim <placeName type="auto_name">Badensis</placeName> sive <placeName type="citizen_name">Thermopolis</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliae</placeName> episcopum reperio, quem mihi d. <persName ref="p8041" cert="high">a Lasco</persName> adiunctum vult.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l552" cert="high">Vilna</placeName> tuae humanitati, quid promoverim, diligenter scripturus sum.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nova non sunt quam de victoria regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Poloniae</placeName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2574" cert="high">Livonenses</placeName>; verum deditio potius quam victoria dici potest, licet coacti se dediderunt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pacis conditiones hae sunt: Sumptus belli, nempe quadraginta milia aureorum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2574" cert="high">Livonenses</placeName> acceperant se daturos; sed rex eis haec munifice condonavit.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Certum numerum equitum regi in militiam dabunt; de numero non constat, quamvis sint, qui putant quatuor quatuor milia, quandocunque iis opus habeat.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Homicidas, qui legatos regis interfecerant, mittent regi <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Poloniae</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid vi aut dolo acceperint a ducatu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l841" cert="high">Lithuanae</placeName>, id omne restituent.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec de conditionibus pacis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caeterum quoniam scio humanit(at)em tuam avide sententiam certam et apertam <persName ref="p2095" cert="high">Melanchthonis</persName> de humanitate Christi expectare, mitto tibi hanc, quam d. <persName ref="p8041" cert="high">a Lasco</persName> mihi describendam dedit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ea est exerpta ex lectionibus viri et dictata, haecque sunt, quae Lutherani eum recantare <placeName ref="l569" cert="high">Wormatiae</placeName> voluerunt.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus det gratiam, ut aperte et palam veritatem tueatur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hic in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonia</placeName> veritas dei optimi maximi benefitio altius radices figit.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nobilitatem docet confidenter d. <persName ref="p8041" cert="high">a Lasco</persName>, hodie per duas horas sermonem habuit de vero et genuino intellectu verborum Christi, hoc est corpus meum in mensa nobilis.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Convertit multos et confirmat veram non lutheranam sententiam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus orandus, ut confirmetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Apud principem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracoviae</placeName> septuagenarium iam fuit, quem eo duxit, ut vere fateatur papam antichristum esse neque quicquam eum moratur quam abusus, in quos vertuntur ecclesiastica bona, et coenae dominicae genuinus intellectus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De bonis ecclesiasticis, ut in pios usus vertantur, facile consentient, paulatimque, ut imbibat verum intellectum verborum Christi, sperat d. <persName ref="p8041" cert="high">a Lasco</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vos commendate utrumque precibus domino.</s>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam si lucrari posset, magna spes est de tota <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonia</placeName> hac minori.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale bene cum familia universa.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec, quaeso, qualiacunque sint, communices d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3988" cert="high">Ioanni Wolfio</persName>, d. <persName type="auto_name">Sebastiano</persName>, tuis generis et nobilibus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Poloniae</placeName>, quibus omnibus offitiosam salutem a me dicito.</s>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p505" cert="high">Burcherus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="31" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Uxorem meam tuo patrocinio commendo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="32" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem ffürnemmen, wysen hern <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heynrych Bullynger</persName>, predicanten, mynem gunstigen hern zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Zurych</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
